, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;发起&lt;/strong&gt;联合军事行动是特朗普政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YlJlkZp4PYMn_dzL2uOySRfHixc5BQpge5jr-i9ImZEPppk_TOQp_tnStu-iVOHrPUoc4Cvtynq2ySJzXVGtEENf5WcO-xOtF5xdwXhPEfK5CWzV0aSYTN2hcMO_7o2hKItARhOyol8CXE8BIEbBJL0XhlHYth-4ZbfymQC6CwU8uTe1l5nQuHGq_JkNI9oT56So5UPebum3DfVL-A8XjUDrEuaKIEEmQe1_Er-2uG-NPlGVirA5ZGv2PK5qyFuOWKHrZYbrVzkT76YhILWcycZr11PpxxGMAG3K-TvmlnPDh-oL7Ekki0LnzEAUlqpx4mUR9XpxTAODHlLSil89yCBU2dpJfC8yVV2hPWrLymORj_vuzsPh_SNJ2bg/TJcWRhTRSxC_Wr5TZgGXfmF_7Zdv8QC5/18" target="_blank"&gt;打击中南美洲贩毒活动的最新举措&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国南方司令部&lt;/strong&gt;称此举是与盟国厄瓜多尔一起“对抗毒品恐怖分子的果断行动”，厄瓜多尔近年来日益成为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LSBJlcNU6khFSRAnXuaoVq8AtbGw6b-p_jZsfFt4t0X_vgHCBUuLs7a6W-AeSiXTAHJ0vOXByjNKIkJlLelmiXQNGmMaHzxvnNmpVg61IttWAwq91YPuSCsKwe98za9vb_4gEn3uOd1sQGRvPZ4GTP2rQ3Auk1EOUvRPc_dWquyvTTWKTxUUBtx8uRTSqoByWykSFlggztgQ4_SC5Zp-yAK-VSzzAUMOPVF2TJ3_GdQoaxUuYxk0X3Sm3qRjLONij2yArcPfiK8vvhW2GuVKXSGTNbzfrH0UXM2h9yjiUYzK18CiHgXB59JjQGJx32Ms1EHlVJhYc57_vmS3NfRrsTGbnNyZomlsO19qQYAM3Z4VD63aWdTD04sgP2w/VElrEIqZXR8MP18RN0grADGdpGc_Oau9/18" target="_blank"&gt;可卡因贸易的暴力中心&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;美国的行动&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;进一步升级，&lt;/strong&gt;其中包括&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Rkqdl3MkwogetA6j5g2eN4YO13D7ZSn18u2zAllDPj3faFTgsJVEwEFYq6zcHpiJwpwBXe-Ek7P5jSDtjLt7B9R0_G_dRlXQY5JtKLc77MOHPt16CYfAlqwpaaRKWl_PD7BrgY-I-6JKucUTW1-9LN00BRHN-u9EBCgnME5LmdvgPBHdfxnvfQ2jsQhalPKzbsXQCaK3Qxff7KPEiyoDvS0wgCHNLQcCKwKfN7GRKN2OA-rb8Yjq9ZvvGpDV-Bm5OfyADPoprm4xF5QG88NaXmT9gi_WWlP-rU-fqSrBjlD2mU9lZU5zic092aXGqnDSDwKtRgrf9HpXP5v_iwD0NcAjWyHuG32m5PYP0_zNrKkNcU-oV5VTwyMIOt8/Om5XKZtKPrg3nLvrKi3p8R2B1kHmdWm_/18" target="_blank"&gt;对太平洋和加勒比海沿岸船只进行了一系列有争议的空袭&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&